{"tid":448444,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有揸過Honda NBox？","createTime":"2017-10-26T08:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T09:13:42.000Z","uid":13222,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"74a4a01b8bb13b1170af86c4eab1bf4881fe8fee","tid":448444,"uid":13222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:29:27.000Z","msg":"因為本身鐘意KCAR<br />\n大家有冇係香港或者日本揸過既經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/162922_4c1a36aef563e4979ec762cea6fc8a44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F162922_4c1a36aef563e4979ec762cea6fc8a44.jpg&h=c51ba626&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3aa75fd6f02375c9586372f18d40477b8f2ecbf2","tid":448444,"uid":68516,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T14:11:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為本身鐘意KCAR<br />\n大家有冇係香港或者日本揸過既經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/162922_4c1a36aef563e4979ec762cea6fc8a44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F162922_4c1a36aef563e4979ec762cea6fc8a44.jpg&h=c51ba626&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己揸緊k car<br />\nNA得五十幾匹 聽到就估佢行唔郁 但係大山 山頂都上到<br />\n如果係行turbo就好好多 turbo既你當自己揸緊1200cc既車到喇<br />\n<br />\n耗油方面你依架一定好過我架10年車 如果你行高速多既話都可以做到18km/l 我自己嗰架入$200蚊大約行到230-270左右 最勁行到310km<br />\n<br />\n泊車一定好過其他車 冇頭冇尾 又窄人一截 非常好泊<br />\n<br />\n因為佢細cc比油都要多啲 平路差唔多二千五轉先開始識郁 行高速既話80km/h大約2500轉 100km/h就要3000左右<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166b62d5218bec0d594d58aa2fcf9d24820b4214","tid":448444,"uid":13222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:22:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為本身鐘意KCAR<br />\n大家有冇係香港或者日本揸過既經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/162922_4c1a36aef563e4979ec762cea6fc8a44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F162922_4c1a36aef563e4979ec762cea6fc8a44.jpg&h=c51ba626&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己揸緊k car<br />\nNA得五十幾匹 聽到就估佢行唔郁 但係大山 山頂都上到<br />\n如果係行turbo就好好多 turbo既你當自己揸緊1200cc既車到喇<br />\n<br />\n耗油方面你依架一定好過我架10年車 如果你行高速多既話都可以做到18km/l 我自己嗰架入$200蚊大約行到230-270左右 最勁行到310km<br />\n<br />\n泊車一定好過其他車 冇頭冇尾 又窄人一截 非常好泊<br />\n<br />\n因為佢細cc比油都要多啲 平路差唔多二千五轉先開始識郁 行高速既話80km/h大約2500轉 100km/h就要3000左右<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好詳細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該巴打"},{"pid":"305e1cc1c0c1fb56b7927d6fbd882576a1c8bc01","tid":448444,"uid":99067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T02:24:01.000Z","msg":"揸過，夠力，但嘈。<br />\n香港660cc 無市場只係牌費問題，用黎做買餸車唔錯。"},{"pid":"49b118894984721d3f75d3908f93736abf8320e0","tid":448444,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T04:35:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揸過，夠力，但嘈。<br />\n香港660cc 無市場只係牌費問題，用黎做買餸車唔錯。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n稅係重點....日本出K Car 平稅平牌費，新車都係&yen;100-130萬。 嚟到香港要廿幾萬港紙<br />\n<br />\nCH-R果啲去到30尾，我真係出部Q2都有找"},{"pid":"9c7c9a0494fad0cabe7f560904a5505333c41a04","tid":448444,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:33:03.000Z","msg":"Nbox真係好靚..<br />\n<br />\n去日本見通街都係<img src=\