moji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/162922_4c1a36aef563e4979ec762cea6fc8a44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F162922_4c1a36aef563e4979ec762cea6fc8a44.jpg&h=c51ba626&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我等多2個星期 就收車日 都係NBOX TURBO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身架車比日本仔改晒包圍避震 全部野包晒約15萬左右 分紙都睇過 黎到香港對過晒 內外都好新<br />\n<br />\n不過kcar 要咁既價 真係唔係個個都覺得ok 不過我就係喜歡玩kcar 所以呢個價算係咁 出邊好多都係14 ~ 16 呢個價 28cae 有部紅色 要28萬添"},{"pid":"0a985e8d3c247c911824ea9f188a662a41c28c5d","tid":448444,"uid":13222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T15:08:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為本身鐘意KCAR<br />\n大家有冇係香港或者日本揸過既經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/162922_4c1a36aef563e4979ec762cea6fc8a44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F162922_4c1a36aef563e4979ec762cea6fc8a44.jpg&h=c51ba626&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我等多2個星期 就收車日 都係NBOX TURBO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身架車比日本仔改晒包圍避震 全部野包晒約15萬左右 分紙都睇過 黎到香港對過晒 內外都好新<br />\n<br />\n不過kcar 要咁既價 真係唔係個個都覺得ok 不過我就係喜歡玩kcar 所以呢個價算係咁 出邊好多都係14 ~ 16 呢個價 28cae 有部紅色 要28萬添</blockquote><br />\n巴打你邊度買<br />\n去日拍網bid？"},{"pid":"0125f5117b423c693